  The commit-op Rev field is dropped (set to ""), so archived events carry no
  rev. Models forgetting to copy a field during struct construction.
expected-detection: |
  CheckInvariants tracks per-DID rev monotonicity, so an empty rev should
  surface as a rev regression. (Note: the final-state Compare no longer
