  and a wrong NON-empty rev is caught there — see m026. An EMPTY rev is
  caught by the monotonicity invariant.) Known dead path in this simulator
  config — see m018 (the hot-path companion); simulator traffic never takes
  the resync fallback this mutates.
expected-tier: default
tiers: default,stress

